#: ../../docs/training_manual/grass/index.rst:3
msgid "Module: GRASS"
msgstr "Modul: GRASS"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/grass/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"GRASS (Geographic Resources Analysis Support System) is a well-known open "
"source GIS with a wide array of useful GIS functions. It was first released "
"in 1984, and has seen much improvement and additional functionality since "
"then. QGIS allows you to make use of GRASS' powerful GIS tools directly."
msgstr ""
"GRASS (Sistem za podršku analizi geografskih resursa) je dobro poznati GIS "
"otvorenog koda sa širokim spektrom korisnih GIS funkcija. Prvi put je "
"objavljen 1984. godine i od tada je doživeo značajna poboljšanja i dodatne "
"funkcionalnosti. QGIS vam omogućava da direktno koristite moćne GIS alate "
"GRASS-a."
